# Location Alarm

Location-based utility app for Android that triggers alarms/notifications when entering or leaving configured geographic areas (geofences).

---

## Table of contents
- Features
- Screenshots
- Requirements
- Build & install
- Permissions
- Usage
- Notes & troubleshooting
- Contributing
- License
- Contact

---

## Features
- Create location-based alarms (geofences) with configurable radius.
- Trigger audible/visual notifications when entering or exiting a geofence.
- Persist saved locations and alarm settings.
- Runs in background (service/foreground-notification) to monitor location.
- Simple UI to add, edit and remove location alarms.

(Adjust or expand features based on actual implementation in app/ if needed.)

